{"tid":1603074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底大家有幾多覺悟？","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T02:27:01.000Z","uid":166734,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e773152c5798050dc081b75daa7545286baa1836","tid":1603074,"uid":166734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:04:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2407171866071045&amp;id=1246772398777670&amp;sfnsn=mo&amp;d=n&amp;vh=e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2407171866071045%26id%3D1246772398777670%26sfnsn%3Dmo%26d%3Dn%26vh%3De&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrXwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=bf3cf5d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2407171866071045&amp;id=1246772398777670&amp;sfnsn=mo&amp;d=n&amp;vh=e</a><br />\n<br />\n每次見狗都係即跑，不但暴露身後弱點，更加失去手足。<br />\n<br />\n明知出去一定面對狗，但係咁驚狗？<br />\n<br />\n即係大家仍然未有勇氣面對。<br />\n<br />\n永遠只係捱打既一方。"},{"pid":"1281cb9ba1b1072cfc596f3eec8f70e04ceb148a","tid":1603074,"uid":104811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"聽日 930 全港三罷"},{"pid":"0ad6b8a882629efa259714191d847084d1571daa","tid":1603074,"uid":248834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:10:09.000Z","msg":"真係恕我直言<br />\n我都係前排變左後排<br />\n次次見到咁樣真係好驚比你地賣<br />\n三個月啦<br />\n鑊鑊都係咁樣雞飛狗走<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"8a4319853de4d5f6de095ca7255d64df14532d5c","tid":1603074,"uid":166734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:13:46.000Z","msg":"其實係呢個時候, 仲適合和里非遊行咩？！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我其實講到好多次，而家係打仗，你出得預左同佢地死過。 逃亡只會慘敗。"},{"pid":"7ee10342914d0f9ac47e6934d6d9c5728de4d2d5","tid":1603074,"uid":311907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:14:40.000Z","msg":"大家係咪唔記得好多野要繼續做？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602820</a>"},{"pid":"1